body: - Fix a bug where projects contained in paths with special regex characters (ie, (, ), $, etc) would break synx.

name: v0.0.5
body:
- synx will abort if there are groups containing a forward slash.
- synx accepts exclusions with or without the leading forward slash in the group path.

name: v0.0.4
body: Fixed a bug where non-native targets would cause synx to crash.

name: v0.0.3
body: - Fixed a bug where synx sometimes tried to create a directory twice.
